Hereâ€™s a **complete Jenkins pipeline job and freestyle job setup** for a **Django project**, covering:

* âœ… Unit Tests
* âœ… Integration Tests
* âœ… Linting (Static Code Analysis)
* âœ… Security Scans (Bandit)
